Author: tibor
Title: 🔥🦊【LIVE】📈FOX TRADING📈 AUTOMATED FOREX & CRYPTO | ARBITRAGE | TRADING POOL 🔥
Body: The reasons to raise are:  Increased Token Demand Based on our experience with Fox Binary Signals, we have determined that interest in our trading algorithm increases every month linked to it’s profitability. Additionally, new users will need to purchase tokens to gain access to services and current users will need to hold it to keep the lifetime access. All these points combined create an unstoppable demand and drive up the price of the FOXT token.  Deflationary token After every payment of FOXT tokens made on the Fox Trading platform by new users, a small amount of those tokens will be burned, making the Fox Trading Token a deflationary currency. This mechanism ensures the growth of Fox Trading token value which will incentivize long-term holding of the currency by investors. . To go lower in value could be on a market draw down like now.

Additionally, new users will need to purchase tokens to gain access to services and current users will need to hold it to keep the lifetime access. All these points combined create an unstoppable demand and drive up the price of the FOXT token.   -Deflationary token After every payment of FOXT tokens made on the Fox Trading platform by new users, a small amount of those tokens will be burned, making the Fox Trading Token a deflationary currency. This mechanism ensures the growth of Fox Trading token value which will incentivize long-term holding of the currency by investors.

Body: Hello, here we compare the two systems  Self-trading  • Low volume of transactions and position fees for each transaction. • A good trader can earn approx. 20% of annual revenue income. • You must have a great deal of trading experience. • You have to waste time monitoring the market. • Take a higher risk of loss than Robot Trading.  Algorithm automated Trading  • In automatic trading of cryptocurrency, if trading volume is high, the trading fee will be equal to 0%. For example, Poloniex and Kraken. • With a good algorithm and a limited number of people using it, Robot Trading has greater profits than self-trading. • It is a stable trading system for profit, so you do not have to waste time watching your screen 24 hours a day. • There are no psychological factors that affect your trades.

Author: MattPumpkin
Title: 🔥🦊【LIVE】📈FOX TRADING📈 AUTOMATED FOREX & CRYPTO | ARBITRAGE | TRADING POOL 🔥
Body: Hello,  Could you expand on how the trading pool works?  From what I could gather from the white paper and the foxtrading.io homepage, a portion of the ICO will go towards a pool that will be used by your algorithm to trade. Those trades will be executed automatically. 75% of the gains from those trades will be paid to token holders as a dividend.  Is that correct?  If that is correct, what happens if the trading algorithm goes red? Do you hold off on dividend payments until the pool is in the green?!  Does your auto-trading feature replicate the trading pool’s decisions, in a separate account for that individual trader? Or is the auto-trading feature personalized?  You say “the automatic trading system means that the trader ‘teaches’ the software what signals to search and how to interpret them”, which sounds fascinating. Though how does that work in practice?  Thank you very much for your time,  Matt

Author: tibor
Title: 🔥🦊【LIVE】📈FOX TRADING📈 AUTOMATED FOREX & CRYPTO | ARBITRAGE | TRADING POOL 🔥
Body: Hello Albermaze.  We are not aiming to be big on that, we will limit the number of users to avoid affecting the market, we don´t want quantity, we want quality of the trades and success of our users.  If you are afraid about the machines, they already exist, they are called high frequency machines and are the ones that control the market on Forex, they are managed by few investors (hedge funds). Have a look here for more info. https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/High-frequency_trading  This is part of the thread on wikipedia:  On the early 2000s, high-frequency trading still accounted for fewer than 10% of equity orders, but this proportion was soon to begin rapid growth. According to data from the NYSE, trading volume grew by about 164% between 2005 and 2009 for which high-frequency trading might be accounted. As of the first quarter in 2009, total assets under management for hedge funds with high-frequency trading strategies were $141 billion, down about 21% from their peak before the worst of the crises, although most of the largest HFT's are actually LLC's owned by a small number of investors. The high-frequency strategy was first made popular by Renaissance Technologies who use both HFT and quantitative aspects in their trading. Many high-frequency firms are market makers and provide liquidity to the market which lowers volatility and helps narrow bid-offer spreads, making trading and investing cheaper for other market participants.  Regards,

Author: tibor
Title: 🔥🦊【LIVE】📈FOX TRADING📈 AUTOMATED FOREX & CRYPTO | ARBITRAGE | TRADING POOL 🔥
Body: Hello Bouriffe  - At some point is Fox Trading going to completely replace this existing offer ? No the existing offer will remain as we have lots of customers using the service. - Do you envisage similar subscription plans for Fox Trading, with the same type of limitations (# of signals, trade size ...) ? Yes we will make monthly or yearly payments with our tokens and limited acess to users. But if you are ICO investor you will have this services for live and free, this is one of the benefits of being ICO investor. - Will payment have to be done exclusively with FXT ? (it could be challenging for your existing user base if you plan to migrate them) The payments of the Fox Signals will remain in USD, the payments for Fox Trading are going to be in FXT tokens, new users that had not participated on the ICO will need to purchase his tokens on the exchanges - White-paper is mentioning some Premium signals > Could you please share more details ? We are defining it but investors of more than 0,5 ETH will have them - I see AutoTrading is already existing, I assume you will setup a segregated pool for FXT Trading Pool ? Yes they are two complete different project one algorithm works in binary options which is only a call or put command and in Forex the algorithm is defining call or put, leverage, trailing stop, and take profit. In the case that you do autotrade by yourself you can change this features depending if you are aggressive or conservative - What are the registration details of your existing business (company details, registration, ...)? Is the FXT ICO ran by this existing company? or by a brand new one? White-paper is not providing any details on this. We are all registered as freelancers as we are working on different places of the world and we are working online, we are waiting to make the company bigger with Fox Trading, the idea is to be registered in Barcelona Spain where we will have the headquarters.

Author: tibor
Title: 🔥🦊【LIVE】📈FOX TRADING📈 AUTOMATED FOREX & CRYPTO | ARBITRAGE | TRADING POOL 🔥
Body: We had planned to upgrade the service to Forex Trading and we were working on the project, but due to the Cryptocurrency boom we also empathize with trading these assets, with which we can generate much more% daily due to the high volatility. Then,we started working to adapt the current algorithm/method to the Forex andCryptocurrencies markets. We wanted to limit this service to a controlled number of users, so, in turn, we decideto take advantage of the Blockchain revolution to create our own ICO. Here comes the idea of offering our investors our own token, FXT, with which they can acquire "part" of our company from which they will receive his investment on ethereum back with the profits from Trading Pool simply holding it, full access to the service for life, and that also offer an interesting possibility of investment as such with which to generate high yields sincethe demand will grow following our algorithm's performance.  Regards,  Fox Trading Team

Title: 🔥🦊【LIVE】📈FOX TRADING📈 AUTOMATED FOREX & CRYPTO | ARBITRAGE | TRADING POOL 🔥
Body: Welcome to Smart Trading!  Join us! and you will receive Exclusive trading services for Forex and Cryptocurrencies    Test alpha version!    WEBSITE  https://foxtrading.io/  RATINGS & PRESS                                                                                               VIDEO          TRANSLATED ANN             English           Russian           Indonesian           Arab            Dutch             Korean             Chinese           Hindi            Portuguese           Japanese             Spanish             French              German             Urdu             Vietnamese             Polski        Join the crowdsale and you'll have access to:  📌 High accuracy trading signals 📌 Trading Pool 📌 Autotrading 100% hands-free        ONE STEP FORWARD FOR THE FOX TRADING TEAM!    Fox Signals A company already working in Forex industry with a big Community  Evolving to cryptoworld. After years working on our first project, Fox Binary Signals, we finally decided to expand our service to offer Forex and Cryptocurrencies trading. From the beginning our goal was to end up offering a complete service for Forex, since in this market we don't have the limitations of capital and disadvantages that Binary Options have. Also, most of our current users are requesting us to change to trading Cryptocurrencies following the nowadays trend. Now is the moment to take this ambitious step forward. Welcome to Smart Trading, welcome to Fox Trading ICO!  Fox Trading Platform. Through a desktop Dashboard and iOS/Android app, ICO investors will get lifetime access to the exclusive and easy to use Fox Trading service, where they will receive signals for trading and also access to the benefits of the Trading Pool, only by holding the tokens. We also offer an Autotrading service to Premium investors where they will be able to copy the system signals automatically in his broker receiving 100% of the benefits.  The services described at the top are going to be payment services, with FXT tokens, for new users which had not participated on the ICO.       +10k         App  Downloads        +1.500         Registered Users       +350% Accumulated Gain        SERVICE FEATURES       FAQ  What is Fox Signals? Where I could find more information about you?  - Fox Signals is a complete functional company that had developed a successful project during 2 years. You can see more about our performance on Fox Signals website or on social media Twitter; Facebook and Instagram.   Why the developers decided to evolve to cryptoworld?  - Main reason is because Binary Options are disappearing due to to unfair brokers, but we also have been motivated because most of our current users are requesting change to Forex trading and cryptocurrency. Finally we have been convinced due to the huge options that provide Blockchain technology and low costs on transactions.    What are the advantages for trading with an Automatic system?  - Trading with an Autotrading platform provides bigger profits than self trading, stable trading system without monitoring and also deletes the psychological effect.   How is the Fox Trading algorithm working?  - Fox Trading algorithm is created by programmers and traders, based on 2 years of results on forex industry, which has been renewed and adapted to Forex and Crypto trading. We have now a BETA version of the robot based on MetaTrader 4 and programmed in mql4.     What are the bullet points of this project?  - All the contributors of Fox Trading will receive directly after project development exclusive trading signals, monthly percentage of benefits of the Trading Pool without adding extra investment and, last but not least, they will have the possibility to use Autotrading services to copy Fox Trading investments in their accounts and receive 100% benefits.   How I can invest on Fox Trading?  - You can purchase tokens on the dashboard after registration and access to your personal account. You will need to provide us first your Ethereum wallet where you will send ETH, this wallet MUST NOT BE from an exchange, in that case you can loose Fox Trading tokens. it will be used to verify your transactions and activate your Fox Trading account when the ICO finishes. Once you send Ethereum to our Crowdsale Contract address you will receive automatically Fox Trading tokens on your wallet.   When is Fox Trading token is going to be transferable?  - You will receive Fox Trading tokens automatically into your wallet after you send ETH to the Crowdsale Contract address. However, Fox Trading tokens are not going to be transferable till the ICO ends. Don't send it or you will lose it.    When is Fox Trading token going to be listed on Exchanges?  - One of the priorities of the team is to list Fox Trading token in most of the exchanges! Social media will be updated once we have new agreements with the exchanges. We are not expecting issues on the listing as we have ERC20 structure which is common in most of the exchanges.       Join the crowdsale and claim your bonus!  https://foxtrading.io/
